This paper is related to the field of Computational Linguistics and specifically focuses on Machine Translation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the use of support vector machines and Naive Bayes Classifier, which are commonly used in the fields of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the performance of the classifiers, which is related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural Networks (cs.NE).
